overWrite

public Config overWrite(Config customConfig)
use this method if Config object is required to have a duplicate copy. Config object should be immutable in order to avoid confusions. It creates a cloned (deep copy) Config object except Config.Data.entity and Config.Data.param (these values are overwritten by Config object an input param)

Parameters:
customConfig - Config.Data.entity and Config.Data.param are used to overwrite to a cloned Config object
Returns:
cloned Config object merged with customConfig
